<i>adverb</i>: 삼가 [삼가], 깍듯이 [깍뜨시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>삼가 [삼가]</dt><br>
<dd>respectfully; courteously; humbly</dd><br>
<dd>조심스럽고 정중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a cautious and polite manner.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깍듯이 [깍뜨시]</dt><br>
<dd>courteously; respectfully</dd><br>
<dd>매우 예의가 바르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very politely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>